ed9790fbadfb38e4d660eb1befd87e803d70dec04d936e8cd26def4a9c21240bb7cae8750ae3395aa4761e6738b9e346c86ba57761cfde30efe46d2cb459a7e4  minio.confd
a53856860189dae66ab970895db10ade8c1857e190bcb68060e4c403c060e91c2db659574329855dc16c49998407402981b7ab331bc93ec814ccdcfce6458d8d  RELEASE.2019-04-18T21-44-59Z.tar.gz"
